---
---

<section class="px-6 py-24 relative overflow-hidden" id="fundamentos">
	<div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-1/3 h-full bg-gradient-to-l from-white/50 to-transparent pointer-events-none"></div>
	<div class="max-w-[1280px] mx-auto relative z-10">
		<div class="text-center mb-20">
			<span class="text-gold font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-xs mb-3 block">Los Fundamentos</span>
			<h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-serif text-text-main">Los 3 Pilares del Método</h2>
		</div>
		<div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 lg:gap-12">
			<div class="bg-white p-10 rounded-[2rem] border border-gray-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-primary/5 transition-all duration-500 group">
				<div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-primary/5 text-primary flex items-center justify-center mb-8 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500">
					<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl font-light">neurology</span>
				</div>
				<h3 class="text-2xl font-serif text-text-main mb-4 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors">Neurociencia Aplicada</h3>
				<p class="text-text-light font-light leading-relaxed mb-6">
					Entender el hardware. Desmitificamos el funcionamiento de tu cerebro bajo presión. Aprendes a identificar cuándo estás en "secuestro amigdalino" y cómo salir de ahí mecánicamente.
				</p>
				<div class="border-t border-gray-100 pt-6">
					<ul class="text-sm text-text-light space-y-3 font-medium">
						<li class="flex gap-3 items-center"><span class="text-gold material-symbols-outlined text-sm">circle</span> Mapeo del Sistema Nervioso</li>
						<li class="flex gap-3 items-center"><span class="text-gold material-symbols-outlined text-sm">circle</span> Neuroplasticidad dirigida</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="bg-white p-10 rounded-[2rem] border border-gray-100 shadow-lg shadow-primary/5 hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-primary/10 transition-all duration-500 md:-translate-y-6 relative z-10 group">
				<div class="absolute inset-0 border-2 border-primary/5 rounded-[2rem] pointer-events-none group-hover:border-primary/20 transition-colors duration-500"></div>
				<div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-primary text-white flex items-center justify-center mb-8 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500 shadow-lg shadow-primary/30">
					<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl font-light">self_improvement</span>
				</div>
				<h3 class="text-2xl font-serif text-text-main mb-4 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors">Psicología Somática</h3>
				<p class="text-text-light font-light leading-relaxed mb-6">
					El cuerpo lleva la cuenta. Las tensiones del liderazgo se acumulan en el tejido fascial y visceral. Utilizamos herramientas somáticas para liberar esa carga "invisible" que nubla tu juicio.
				</p>
				<div class="border-t border-gray-100 pt-6">
					<ul class="text-sm text-text-light space-y-3 font-medium">
						<li class="flex gap-3 items-center"><span class="text-gold material-symbols-outlined text-sm">circle</span> Liberación de Trauma Somático</li>
						<li class="flex gap-3 items-center"><span class="text-gold material-symbols-outlined text-sm">circle</span> Regulación Vagal</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="bg-white p-10 rounded-[2rem] border border-gray-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-primary/5 transition-all duration-500 group">
				<div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-primary/5 text-primary flex items-center justify-center mb-8 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500">
					<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl font-light">schedule</span>
				</div>
				<h3 class="text-2xl font-serif text-text-main mb-4 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors">Protocolos de Eficacia</h3>
				<p class="text-text-light font-light leading-relaxed mb-6">
					Diseño de estilo de vida. No sirve de nada meditar 20 minutos si las otras 15 horas son un caos. Integramos micro-protocolos en tu agenda ejecutiva sin alterar tu productividad.
				</p>
				<div class="border-t border-gray-100 pt-6">
					<ul class="text-sm text-text-light space-y-3 font-medium">
						<li class="flex gap-3 items-center"><span class="text-gold material-symbols-outlined text-sm">circle</span> Higiene Dopaminérgica</li>
						<li class="flex gap-3 items-center"><span class="text-gold material-symbols-outlined text-sm">circle</span> Ritmos Ultradianos</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
